# Unify Course Data Architecture

## Problem

Three independent data sources for "courses":

| Source | Used By | Count |
|---|---|---|
| [courseData.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/data/courseData.ts) (hardcoded) | Public website, course-pricing admin, old finance/fees | 22 |
| [Program](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/admin/AcademicManager.tsx#11-18) model (MongoDB) | `/admin/courses` panel | client added more |
| [CoursePricing](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/CoursePricing.ts#3-15) model (MongoDB) | `/admin/fees` page | mirrors courseData only |

This means:
- New courses added in admin panel don't appear on fee management
- Pricing edited in fee management doesn't sync with admin courses panel
- Public website always shows exactly 22 hardcoded courses regardless

## Solution: Unify on [Program](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/admin/AcademicManager.tsx#11-18) Model

The [Program](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/admin/AcademicManager.tsx#11-18) model already has an embedded [pricing](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/admin/course-pricing) sub-document with `totalFee`, `offerPrice`, `isOfferActive`, etc. Make everything read from [Program](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/admin/AcademicManager.tsx#11-18).

## Proposed Changes

---

### Fee Management

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/(admin)/admin/fees/page.tsx)
- Read courses from `/api/admin/courses` (Program collection) instead of [/api/admin/fees/course](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/fees/course) (CoursePricing)
- Use `course.pricing.totalFee` as base fee, `course.pricing.offerPrice` as offer price
- Update fee → PATCH `/api/admin/courses/{id}` updating `pricing.totalFee`
- Bulk assign still creates [StudentFee](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/StudentFee.ts#11-31) records but using Program-based pricing

#### [MODIFY] [route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/fees/course/route.ts)
- GET: Read from [Program](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/admin/AcademicManager.tsx#11-18) instead of [CoursePricing](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/CoursePricing.ts#3-15)
- PATCH: Update `Program.pricing.totalFee` instead of `CoursePricing.originalPrice`
- POST (assign): Look up pricing from [Program](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/admin/AcademicManager.tsx#11-18) instead of [CoursePricing](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/CoursePricing.ts#3-15)

---

### Public Website

#### [MODIFY] [courses/page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/(public)/courses/page.tsx)
- Fetch courses from `/api/public/courses` (new API reading [Program](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/admin/AcademicManager.tsx#11-18) model) instead of importing `courseData`
- This way new courses added by client appear automatically

#### [NEW] [/api/public/courses/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/public/courses/route.ts)
- Returns all active [Program](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/admin/AcademicManager.tsx#11-18) docs, sorted by `displayOrder`
- Public endpoint, no auth needed

#### [MODIFY] [courses/[id]/page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/(public)/courses/[id]/page.tsx)
- Fetch single course from `/api/public/courses/{code}` instead of `courseData.find()`

---

### Admin Navigation Cleanup

#### [MODIFY] [Sidebar.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/layout/Sidebar.tsx)
- Remove separate "Course Pricing" link (if present) — pricing is now inside Courses panel
- Keep "Fee Management" for student fee assignments and tracking

